Class InterchainTokenServiceClient

InterchainTokenServiceClient

Description

Type-safe contract client for InterchainTokenService

Example

import { sepolia } from "viem/chains";

const client = createInterchainTokenServiceClient({
 chain: sepolia,
 address: "0x1234..."
});
